# AIRA Clinical Workflow: System Proposal

## Overview
AIRA Clinical Workflow is an AI-powered Electronic Health Record (EHR) system designed to streamline clinical documentation, enhance OCR accuracy, and ensure HIPAA-compliant patient care.

## Key Features
- **Intelligent Documentation**: AI-powered clinical note generation (transcription to structured notes).
- **High-Accuracy OCR**: 98% accuracy for digitizing prescriptions and lab reports.
- **Efficient Workflow**: Average clinical note documentation time reduced to under 3 minutes.
- **HIPAA Compliant**: Enterprise-grade security and data privacy standards.

